345
00:23:19,666 --> 00:23:21,699
How would I know if something
was up with you?

346
00:23:21,767 --> 00:23:23,868
You wouldn't.

347
00:23:23,936 --> 00:23:28,773
But I would tell you if you
asked me. Return the favor?

348
00:23:28,840 --> 00:23:32,710
Meet Roger and Marilyn Brunner.

