376
00:25:01,794 --> 00:25:05,530
Not you.

377
00:25:05,598 --> 00:25:08,834
Still, you seem more betrayed
by Jack than by your own body.

378
00:25:10,770 --> 00:25:13,905
I don't feel betrayed by Jack.

379
00:25:13,973 --> 00:25:17,608
And there's no point in being
mad at cancer for being cancer.

380
00:25:17,676 --> 00:25:19,076
Sure there is.

381
00:25:19,143 --> 00:25:21,946
Cancer isn't cruel.

382
00:25:22,013 --> 00:25:26,049
Tiny cell wanders off
from my liver, gets lost,

383
00:25:26,117 --> 00:25:28,051
