384
00:25:28,119 --> 00:25:31,053
where it's just trying
to do its job and...

385
00:25:31,121 --> 00:25:33,255
Grow a liver.

386
00:25:33,323 --> 00:25:37,760
What it grows and where it's
growing it will likely kill you.

387
00:25:37,828 --> 00:25:40,229
Not likely.

388
00:25:40,297 --> 00:25:42,732
It will kill me,

389
00:25:42,800 --> 00:25:48,036
and no amount of blueberries or
antioxidants can change that now.

390
00:25:48,104 --> 00:25:51,439
But you hold Jack accountable for
his inability to cure cancer.

391
00:25:53,877 --> 00:25:56,244
Should I have said
his inability to save you?

392
00:25:56,312 --> 00:26:02,217
Would that be more accurate?
I am slowly shrinking,

393
00:26:02,284 --> 00:26:06,120
while this tiny thing grows
larger every day.

394
00:26:08,123 --> 00:26:10,658
And yet I feel fine.

395
00:26:10,726 --> 00:26:13,460
You will feel fine...

396
00:26:13,529 --> 00:26:15,963
