you don't.

397
00:26:16,031 --> 00:26:21,635
It's a... really very
dull story, though, isn't it?

398
00:26:21,702 --> 00:26:26,973
The ending is always the same,
and that same is that it ends.

399
00:26:27,041 --> 00:26:31,344
So, you withdraw

400
00:26:31,412 --> 00:26:34,514
from your relationship
with your husband,

401
00:26:34,581 --> 00:26:37,082
the man who strolled along
the quays of Livorno, Italy,

402
00:26:37,150 --> 00:26:39,785
and called you Bella.

