00:27:57,337 --> 00:27:59,940
It's difficult to lie still
and fear going to sleep.

405
00:28:00,007 --> 00:28:02,942
What is there to think about?

406
00:28:03,009 --> 00:28:05,243
You listen to your breathing
in the dark

407
00:28:05,311 --> 00:28:07,680
and the tiny clicks
of your blinking eyes.

408
00:28:07,747 --> 00:28:10,549
I dream more now
than I used to.

409
00:28:10,617 --> 00:28:12,417
Well, your dreams were
the one place you could be

