00:28:12,485 --> 00:28:15,955
physically safe, relinquishing
control. Not anymore.

411
00:28:16,022 --> 00:28:18,456
Yeah, I thought about zipping
myself up into a sleeping bag

412
00:28:18,523 --> 00:28:20,758
before I go to sleep,
but it, heh,

413
00:28:20,826 --> 00:28:23,461
sounds like a poor man's
straightjacket.

