428
00:29:12,675 --> 00:29:14,743
You accept the impossibility
of such a feeling,

429
00:29:14,810 --> 00:29:17,045
whereas the angel maker is
still chasing it.

430
00:29:17,113 --> 00:29:20,882
If he got close to it,
that's why he will

