00:29:25,720 --> 00:29:30,924
Instead you find yourself in a
behavior pattern you can't break.

434
00:29:30,992 --> 00:29:33,426
You realize you have a choice.

435
00:29:33,494 --> 00:29:35,495
What is it?

436
00:29:35,563 --> 00:29:40,299
Angel maker will be destroyed by
what's happening inside his head;

437
00:29:40,367 --> 00:29:42,401
You don't have to be.

438
00:29:51,211 --> 00:29:53,112
Did you just smell me?

