476
00:31:59,389 --> 00:32:02,744
To see him slip away.
He lost himself.

477
00:32:03,334 --> 00:32:04,827
And they lost a father.

478
00:32:05,837 --> 00:32:09,373
I thought that
as he got weaker,

479
00:32:09,441 --> 00:32:13,678
as the cancer got worse,
that it would be less confusing

480
00:32:13,745 --> 00:32:17,448
for them.
They could just see him

481
00:32:17,516 --> 00:32:20,350
as a sick man

482
00:32:20,418 --> 00:32:23,620
